# 📊 HR Admin Dashboard Wireframes

## 💻 Desktop View
The desktop dashboard is designed for comprehensive data visibility and efficient management.

### 🔹 Key Sections

#### 🧭 Sidebar Navigation
- Dashboard  
- Employees  
- Recruitment  
- Performance  
- Settings  

#### 📈 Dashboard Overview
- Total Employees  
- Active Jobs  
- New Applications  
- Performance Metrics  

#### 📋 Employee Management
- Employee list (table format)  
- Search and filter options  
- Add / Edit / Remove employees  

#### 📅 Recruitment Panel
- Job postings  
- Candidate tracking  
- Application status  

#### 🔔 Notifications Panel
- Alerts for new applicants  
- System updates  

---

## 📱 Mobile View
The mobile dashboard is optimized for quick access and simplified navigation.

### 🔹 Key Sections

#### ☰ Collapsible Menu
- Hamburger menu for navigation  

#### 📊 Summary Cards
- Key metrics (Employees, Jobs, Applications)  

#### 📋 Employee List
- Scrollable list view  
- Quick actions (view/edit)  

#### 🔔 Notifications
- Real-time alerts  

#### ➕ Quick Actions
- Add Employee  
- Post Job  

---

## 🧠 Design Approach
- Low-fidelity (Lo-Fi) wireframes  
- Focus on:  
  - Clear user flow  
  - Functional layout  
  - Easy navigation across devices  
- Responsive thinking (Desktop + Mobile)  
- Minimal styling (grayscale, placeholders)  

---

